sentences: Titti Sigrid Renée Eliasson Sjöblom (born 29 August 1949) is a Swedish pop singer.
She participated at Melodifestivalen 1974 with the song "Fröken Ur-sång", ending up in fourth place.
Hyllning till Höga Kusten with Ehrling Eliasson. 2006
Titti & Ehrling sjunger Kai Gullmar with Ehrling Eliasson. 2008
